OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fat first this evening, but thickening
OL,7,Fcloud and patchy light rain
OL,8,Fdeveloping. Occasional mist and
OL,9,Fdrizzle overnight with winds light
OL,10,Ffrom the southwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA cloudy start with patchy
OL,13,Flight rain and drizzle. Soon mainly
OL,14,Fdry and skies brightening, perhaps the
OL,15,Fodd sunny break developing. Feeling
OL,16,Fpleasant in light to moderate
OL,17,Fsouthwest winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
