OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA dry
OL,6,Fstart on Wednesday, but rain pushing
OL,7,Fin from the northwest. Rain or showers
OL,8,Fon Thursday and Friday, which may be
OL,9,Fheavy. Winds strengthening on Friday,
OL,10,Fgales possible.
